data.description: This one has it all! END UNIT Located on a quite tree lined block of homeowners. TOTAL REHAB in 2016. Includes 4 SPACIOUS bedrooms & 3 full baths, including one full bathroom on the main level!  Improvements include hardwood floors, SS appliances, granite counters, under mount sink, walnut cabinets, ceiling fans and KITCHEN ISLAND. Walk onto your INVITING DECK off the master suite, which has its own EN-SUITE BATH and jetted tub. Basically a new house with complete new PLUMBING, HVAC, AND ELECTRIC, ROOF, AND DECK as well, all in 2016! Worry free and low maintenance, Close to multiple shopping and dining, and walking distance to Leakin Park with miles of hiking trail and great for biking. Close to 40 and 83. A must see!!!
